{"tid":464102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嫌老公生意失敗，老婆買兇殺夫點知中伏","createTime":"2017-11-10T07:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T08:11:33.000Z","uid":75969,"like":907,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":95,"replies":[{"pid":"d44e95183c1dea8e0cacd7d6b45bd37be324b6b8","tid":464102,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/155001_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F155001_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=d3edb3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國德州一名女子與丈夫只能共富貴，不能共患難，丈夫事業失意時，不但提出離婚，還想買兇殺夫謀財，最終被夫拆穿詭計。<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報導，這名50歲來自波多黎各的美國公民索薩（Ramon Sosa），失婚之後於2007年邂逅43歲墨西哥女子露露（Maria Lulu），被對方美色所迷。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>露露每幾個月要返鄉續領簽證，希望嫁個美國公民取得永久居留權</strong></span>，2人認識3年後結婚。<br />\n <br />\n報導中說，索薩抱得女神歸，一直十分恩愛，但到2015年出現問題。索薩經營的健身房出現財務困難，露露就提出要離婚。<br />\n <br />\n到當年中旬，索薩收到朋友兼拳擊徒弟古斯塔沃（Gustavo）「報料」，指露露想買兇殺他。索薩以為古斯塔沃只是開玩笑，但古斯塔沃說，露露的確找他談過，而且十分認真，曾以手比槍指著自己的頭。索薩相信，露露當時不知古斯塔沃是他的徒弟。<br />\n <br />\n索薩半信半疑，於是安排古斯塔沃再約露露見面，並偷錄兩人對話。古斯塔沃再約見露露，訛稱認識2名殺手，露露果然表示有興趣。<br />\n <br />\n索薩這時不得不信，就將錄音交給警方。警方叫他先裝死，他照做，在聯邦調查局和德州騎警協助下，他扮成太陽穴中槍，倒臥在沙漠淺坑。<br />\n <br />\n警方拍照之後，安排索薩入住酒店，同時派扮成殺手的臥底探員，將索薩的屍照給露露看，她見丈夫「死狀」後露出笑容。<br />\n <br />\n不過，笑到最後的是索薩。警方以教唆謀殺罪拘捕露露，她去年被判監20年。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171110/1238371/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171110%2F1238371%2F&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=de8dae0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171110%2F1238371%2F&h=fd5a7de3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171110/1238371/</a>"},{"pid":"5a16807afbc8d76a829e6d6ad21e60757bbbdc61","tid":464102,"uid":75969,"like":445,"dislike":1,"score":444,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"好似睇戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17d13a85b290b7c5512801579414afec7e84cfc","tid":464102,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73a6a7f47c0feb96534e08962a100dddc0ed72ad","tid":464102,"uid":706,"like":347,"dislike":3,"score":344,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"好兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9544098988c0929409cfe85816691ce25e7eb25a","tid":464102,"uid":81271,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"呢個女人好恐怖"},{"pid":"6810c5901f7200a8f7bf1cba310c231efd766e66","tid":464102,"uid":126100,"like":38,"dislike":37,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:59:19.000Z","msg":"真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明一早拉得仲搞咁多野拍戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5836cc59e6d425d55e9db17bf13b300441f39a3d","tid":464102,"uid":44277,"like":75,"dislike":4,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"美色?"},{"pid":"3f3892af76ea6687221eea5e02a4e730f6c671c3","tid":464102,"uid":522,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"墨西哥女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37ab88b8cfcb7d7e88a27534efd24ebeb13db9d","tid":464102,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接拉佢？"},{"pid":"01c00ebcaa4e27c7e518a3faf26921283e70615a","tid":464102,"uid":53687,"like":205,"dislike":0,"score":205,"citedB