":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:40:34.000Z","msg":"當佢比人拉果陣係咩表情<br />\n當下會有咩講"},{"pid":"9057e721a47f4dc5805b1f9f5501ab772adc95d9","tid":464102,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:41:56.000Z","msg":"一日為師 終身為父"},{"pid":"0c099f5ed1523bd81b10881ec3ae49078d743e94","tid":464102,"uid":12565,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:44:17.000Z","msg":"引以為鑑<br />\n老公=香港人<br />\n美國公民權=香港護照<br />\n老婆=大陸女人"},{"pid":"a34edeeb62a5fa86658befccda7cc71e5ca8709e","tid":464102,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>啲女人好撚古惑架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nDV都唔洗出動</blockquote><br />\n佢蠢啦，唔係女廁傾</blockquote><br />\n邊鳩都傾都一樣"},{"pid":"79dd6d89cf7bca521fa38b1575d431ba8acd9971","tid":464102,"uid":4813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但其實如果唔係老公裝佢弓弩<br />\n個老婆就買唔到兇殺人<br />\n咁就唔存在真係買兇殺人嘅行為 只係個人ff<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都告得企圖謀殺"},{"pid":"7537dcd2126270f4b7670b82b9d55f265fdf81ab","tid":464102,"uid":43009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/155001_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F155001_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=d3edb3a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國德州一名女子與丈夫只能共富貴，不能共患難，丈夫事業失意時，不但提出離婚，還想買兇殺夫謀財，最終被夫拆穿詭計。<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果日報》報導，這名50歲來自波多黎各的美國公民索薩（Ramon Sosa），失婚之後於2007年邂逅43歲墨西哥女子露露（Maria Lulu），被對方美色所迷。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>露露每幾個月要返鄉續領簽證，希望嫁個美國公民取得永久居留權</strong></span>，2人認識3年後結婚。<br />\n <br />\n報導中說，索薩抱得女神歸，一直十分恩愛，但到2015年出現問題。索薩經營的健身房出現財務困難，露露就提出要離婚。<br />\n <br />\n到當年中旬，索薩收到朋友兼拳擊徒弟古斯塔沃（Gustavo）「報料」，指露露想買兇殺他。索薩以為古斯塔沃只是開玩笑，但古斯塔沃說，露露的確找他談過，而且十分認真，曾以手比槍指著自己的頭。索薩相信，露露當時不知古斯塔沃是他的徒弟。<br />\n <br />\n索薩半信半疑，於是安排古斯塔沃再約露露見面，並偷錄兩人對話。古斯塔沃再約見露露，訛稱認識2名殺手，露露果然表示有興趣。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">索薩這時不得不信，就將錄音交給警方。警方叫他先裝死，他照做，在聯邦調查局和德州騎警協助下，他扮成太陽穴中槍，倒臥在沙漠淺坑。</span><br />\n <br />\n警方拍照之後，安排索薩入住酒店，同時派扮成殺手的臥底探員，將索薩的屍照給露露看，她見丈夫「死狀」後露出笑容。<br />\n <br />\n不過，笑到最後的是索薩。警方以教唆謀殺罪拘捕露露，她去年被判監20年。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171110/1238371/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171110%2F1238371%2F&d=mra2Gp7%2BDn3%2B5CFdgs%2Bt7EbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=de8dae0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20171110%2F1238371%2F&h=fd5a7de3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20171110/1238371/</a></blockquote><br />\nd差佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港果d實話證據不足唔撚理</blockquote><br />\n唔好羨慕住<br />\n美國好興釣魚執法<br />\n呢單啲差佬其實做返佢地平時做既野"},{"pid":"8cab562bf8934794fef03117a5a5299200fd014d","tid":464102,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T10:00:44.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9adc8510dbc14080081fdb74941da25b3bf847e9","tid":464102,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T10:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明一早拉得仲搞咁多野拍戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n攞證據"},{"pid":"77a09659bb82df05ad990e7c6c21d5f6778010da","tid":464102,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同其他女人一樣，都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 